{
  "stem": "24171.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my sister's boy, he was about 11 or 12 years old, the oldest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And other kind of 13-, 14-, 15-year-old boys kind of got together from the family and everybody got like, take my carts too and bring for me a pound or two or whatever bread.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But when they came-- it's just kind of like about two, three kilometers before that village, before [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Polyana. ?] I had a brother living there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I have the picture there from their house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when they came, there was a bridge with a river and the bridge to go to, and there was already the gendarme.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They didn't let in already in that thing because they were over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- Barry was living there, my husband, in that direction, after that village, after [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Polyana, ?] so-- like a couple kilometers after that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were already rounding up there the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they came back and-- and said that they are not letting in in there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so my father-- maybe my father knew more from the sheriff, just didn't told us-- because I remember I was-- it was, you know, right away after Pesach.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The spring is coming and in the backyard there was-- through the winter and the snow or whatever it was, an old-- those big plums tree fell down so we went to clean up the backyard for the summer.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were other of all kinds, apple trees and things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as my father was holding on one side the big log from that tree to bring it out down from-- there was a little hill, and I was in the other side.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he came around to hold my sister's boy-- boy and said they won't let us in there.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
